u are riding and are happy to share them with our readers around&nbsp;the world here on the Pic Of The Day. Send in your pics&nbsp;with a description&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:kristi@bikerumor.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Kristi Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"49aee33a575a87b97918ac2e3531a9f07935760630ac6184e8714647f8af4f47","category":"Cycling"}